Canada : AB, BC, MB, NB*, NL, NS*, NT, NU*, ON, QC, SK*, YT*. USA : AK, CA, CO, DC*, IA, IL, MA, MD*, MI, NC*, NY, OH, PA*, SC*. Widespread in Palaearctic (
Cerny et al 2020
).

